# Styling

## Single stylesheet

All app styling is in **`app/globals.css`** (~1200 lines). Do not add Tailwind classes to JSX.

## Theme

- Dark construction QA UI: `#060612` background, purple accent `#7c3aed`, amber/orange for Alex guide (`#f59e0b`).
- Clerk auth: shared theme in `lib/clerk-appearance.ts` + `.auth-*` / `.login-*` classes.

## New UI

- Reuse existing class names (`.gen-btn`, `.sidebar`, `.tc-card`, `.guide-*`) before inventing new ones.
- Keep responsive breakpoints consistent with existing `@media` blocks in `globals.css`.

## Alex guide

Character image: `public/alex-engineer.png`. Guide styles prefixed with `.guide-` and `.engineer-`.
